<i>everything that I'm
feeling right now,</i>

51:18.320 --> 51:21.244
<i>and I know Claire
feels exactly the same.</i>

51:21.320 --> 51:24.164
<i>CLAIRE: Peter was
very special to us.</i>

51:25.120 --> 51:28.761
<i>A sort of magnetic presence that
electrified everyone he touched.</i>

51:28.840 --> 51:30.604
<i>And my husband
and I became very</i>

51:30.680 --> 51:32.842
<i>close to him in
the past several months.</i>

51:33.440 --> 51:36.011
<i>Peter was more than a
colleague, more than a friend.</i>

51:36.520 --> 51:38.602
<i>He was family.</i>

51:38.760 --> 51:41.445
<i>Our hearts go out to his
children and to his mother,</i>

