51:46.400 --> 51:48.528
<i>their privacy and
honor their loss.</i>

51:48.600 --> 51:50.204
<i>Today is indeed
a sad day</i>

51:50.280 --> 51:51.964
<i>for the United
States Congress,</i>

51:52.080 --> 51:55.050
